[{"updatedAt":"2026-06-12T21:53:25.109Z","createdAt":"2026-06-12T21:53:25.109Z","id":"qZoccYs1nosn5FNa","name":"HR Onboarding Agent — Governed Mock SaaS Workflow v4","description":null,"active":true,"isArchived":false,"nodes":[{"id":"main-description","name":"Main Description","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[-740,-520],"parameters":{"width":640,"height":300,"content":"## HR Onboarding Agent — Governed Mock SaaS Workflow v4\n\nThis workflow is adapted from a generic employee-provisioning template, but all direct credential-based SaaS provisioning has been removed.\n\nIt demonstrates the candidate-exercise requirements:\n\n1. New employee onboarding trigger.\n2. HR mock lookup for role, level, department, manager, and status.\n3. Training mock lookup for T1-T4 status.\n4. Deterministic role-level + peer-pattern access recommendation.\n5. Employee access-selection simulation.\n6. Manager approval request.\n7. Pre-approval ITSM ticket attempt that must be blocked.\n8. ITSM ticket creation only after approved manager state.\n9. Final onboarding status and audit-event retrieval.\n\nNo real Google Workspace, Slack, Jira, Salesforce, Gmail, Workday, Okta, Entra, OpenAI, or Gemini credentials are required.\n\nv4 focuses on n8n import/runtime compatibility: standard Webhook, Set, HTTP Request, IF, Switch, and Sticky Note nodes only; no credential nodes."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"mock-boundary","name":"Mock Boundary / No Paid Services","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[-740,500],"parameters":{"width":640,"height":500,"content":"## Mock Boundary / No Paid Services\n\nAll external SaaS behavior is represented by local FastAPI mock endpoints.\n\nReal in prototype:\n- n8n orchestration\n- FastAPI HTTP calls\n- deterministic policy/approval/ticket gate behavior in backend\n- PostgreSQL state/audit\n- Ollama or fallback message generation through backend\n\nMocked:\n- HR platform\n- Slack messages\n- Training/LMS\n- Salesforce access target\n- ITSM/Jira/ServiceNow ticketing\n\nNot implemented:\n- real access granting\n- real SaaS provisioning\n- paid hosted model calls\n- direct database writes from n8n","color":4},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"approval-gate-evidence","name":"Approval Gate Evidence","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[700,-320],"parameters":{"width":610,"height":250,"content":"## Approval Gate Evidence\n\nThis workflow intentionally attempts ITSM ticket creation before manager approval.\n\nExpected result: backend blocks the request.\n\nThen the workflow routes based on approval_action:\n- approve -> approved branch, ticket created\n- reject -> rejected status, no ticket\n- expire -> expired status, no ticket\n- pending -> pending status, no ticket\n- wrong_manager -> wrong-manager decision blocked, no ticket\n\nThe approved branch is the only branch that creates the final ITSM ticket.","color":5},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"n8n-compat-notes","name":"n8n Compatibility / Import Notes","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[700,500],"parameters":{"color":6,"width":620,"height":360,"content":"## n8n Compatibility / Import Notes\n\nThis v4 export intentionally uses only standard credential-free nodes:\n\n- Webhook\n- Set\n- HTTP Request\n- IF\n- Switch\n- Sticky Note\n\nExpected local backend base URL: http://api:8000 inside Docker Compose.\n\nExpected demo body:\n\n{\n  \"employee_id\": \"emp_001\",\n  \"selected_systems\": [\"Salesforce\", \"Gong\", \"Sales Slack Channels\"],\n  \"approval_action\": \"approve\"\n}\n\nSupported approval_action values: approve, reject, expire, pending, wrong_manager.\n\nBackward compatible: auto_approve_manager=true maps to approve, false to pending."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"webhook","name":"Webhook - New Hire","type":"n8n-nodes-base.webhook","position":[250,300],"parameters":{"path":"hr-onboarding/new-hire","httpMethod":"POST","responseMode":"responseNode","options":{},"respondTo":"Return Final Result"},"typeVersion":2.1,"webhookId":"f1cb3cca-0529-4566-ad49-054d1e0dbeb0"},{"id":"normalize-input","name":"Normalize Demo Input","type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","position":[450,300],"parameters":{"options":{},"assignments":{"assignments":[{"id":"employee_id","name":"employee_id","type":"string","value":"={{ $json.body?.employee_id || $json.employee_id || 'emp_001' }}"},{"id":"api_base_url","name":"API_BASE_URL","type":"string","value":"={{ $json.body?.api_base_url || $json.api_base_url || $env.API_BASE_URL || 'http://api:8000' }}"},{"id":"selected_systems","name":"selected_systems","type":"array","value":"={{ $json.body?.selected_systems || $json.selected_systems || ['Salesforce','Gong','Sales Slack Channels'] }}"},{"id":"correlation_id","name":"correlation_id","type":"string","value":"={{ $json.body?.correlation_id || 'corr_' + $now.toMillis() }}"},{"id":"actor","name":"actor","type":"string","value":"n8n-hr-onboarding-workflow"},{"id":"auto_approve","name":"auto_approve_manager","type":"boolean","value":"={{ $json.body?.auto_approve_manager ?? $json.auto_approve_manager ?? null }}"},{"id":"approval_action","name":"approval_action","type":"string","value":"={{ $json.body?.approval_action || $json.approval_action || 'approve' }}"},{"id":"demo_note","name":"demo_note","type":"string","value":"={{ $json.body?.demo_note || 'happy_path_with_gate_evidence' }}"}]},"includeOtherFields":true},"typeVersion":3.4},{"id":"start-session","name":"Start Onboarding Session","type":"n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest","position":[650,300],"parameters":{"method":"POST","url":"={{ $node['Normalize Demo Input'].json['API_BASE_URL'] }}/onboarding/start/{{ $node['Normalize Demo Input'].json['employee_id'] }}","sendBody":true,"bodyParameters":{"parameters":[{"name":"correlation_id","value":"={{ $node['Normalize Demo Input'].json['correlation_id'] }}"}]}},"typeVersion":4.2},{"id":"hr-profile","name":"HR Mock: Get Profile","type":"n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest","position":[850,300],"parameters":{"method":"GET","url":"={{ $node['Normalize Demo Input'].json['API_BASE